- I'm so sorry.

753
00:42:25.109 --> 00:42:26.810
Hey. how are you?

754
00:42:26.877 --> 00:42:28.545
Look at her.

755
00:42:28.612 --> 00:42:31.982
She's already
becoming a robot.
like the rest of us.

756
00:42:32.049 --> 00:42:33.617
<i>I'm so sorry</i>
<i>about your grandma.</i>

757
00:42:33.684 --> 00:42:35.419
Well. at least
she didn't suffer.

758
00:42:35.486 --> 00:42:37.321
