she didn't mince words.

812
00:46:20.777 --> 00:46:24.047
Between brain and mouth.
there was no interlocutor.

813
00:46:36.527 --> 00:46:38.295
Anthony Jr.

814
00:46:40.230 --> 00:46:42.432
I don't know what to say.

815
00:46:42.499 --> 00:46:43.834
Come on.

816
00:46:43.901 --> 00:46:46.036
Lay off him. Janice.
Move on.

817
00:46:48.238 --> 00:46:49.873
<i>She was my best friend.</i>

818
00:46:57.748 --> 00:47:01.518
If anybody died
or was in the hospital.

819
00:47:01.585 --> 00:47:06.290
I could be sure I'd get a call
from Lee letting me know.

820
00:47:14.531 --> 00:47:15.832
Thank you. Fanny.

821
00:47:15.899 --> 00:47:17.201
Thank you.

822
00:47:24.274 --> 00:47:25.943
Okay.

823
00:47:26.009 --> 00:47:27.511
What's good for the goose...

824
00:47:31.048 --> 00:47:32.883
Well. most of you
will probably remember

825
00:47:32.950 --> 00:47:37.688
that I have an extraordinary
visual sense.

826
00:47:37.754 --> 00:47:39.189
When I was a child.

827
00:47:39.256 --> 00:47:41.858
