on those laurels.

828
00:47:41.925 --> 00:47:44.861
She didn't flatter me.

829
00:47:48.398 --> 00:47:54.538
She believed that wild flowers
blossomed best among the rocks.

830
00:47:54.605 --> 00:47:56.273
With little water.

831
00:47:57.641 --> 00:47:59.243
But she was tough.

832
00:48:00.410 --> 00:48:02.746
But she was right.

833
00:48:06.016 --> 00:48:08.185
And she's the reason
