864
00:50:24.755 --> 00:50:26.223
I got a beaut.

865
00:50:26.289 --> 00:50:27.257
Artie.

866
00:50:29.559 --> 00:50:30.927
Artie!

867
00:50:30.994 --> 00:50:33.397
Artie. don't talk about that.

868
00:50:33.463 --> 00:50:35.098
<i>Mrs. Soprano may have passed.</i>

869
00:50:35.165 --> 00:50:36.967
<i>but who's to say there
isn't another Mrs. Soprano</i>

870
00:50:37.033 --> 00:50:39.669
just like her.
or will be?

871
00:50:39.736 --> 00:50:43.373
Maybe not with the same
fears and paranoia.

872
00:50:43.440 --> 00:50:45.609
<i>but the same.</i>

873
00:50:50.580 --> 00:50:52.416
What I'm saying is...

874
00:51:00.891 --> 00:51:02.159
<i>Thank you. Chris.</i>

875
00:51:02.225 --> 00:51:03.794
<i>Thank you.</i>

876
00:51:11.435 --> 00:51:12.669
<i> Um...</i>

877
00:51:15.305 --> 00:51:17.808
This is such a crock of shit.

878
00:51:17.874 --> 00:51:19.176
- Carmela.
- I'm sitting here

879
00:51:19.242 --> 00:51:20.911
