protect my children

880
00:51:20.977 --> 00:51:23.814
<i>from the truth about their
grandmother on the one hand.</i>

881
00:51:23.880 --> 00:51:25.449
On the other.
I'm saying to myself.

882
00:51:25.515 --> 00:51:28.151
"What kind of example
am I setting?"

883
00:51:29.119 --> 00:51:31.154
<i>Evading and smiling.</i>

884
00:51:31.221 --> 00:51:33.156
<i>passing out cheese puffs</i>

885
00:51:33.223 --> 00:51:36.893
