886
00:51:36.960 --> 00:51:39.963
Who spread no cheer at all.

887
00:51:40.030 --> 00:51:41.164
Carmela. be quiet.

888
00:51:41.231 --> 00:51:42.899
This is my house!

889
00:51:42.966 --> 00:51:44.501
- I'm leaving.
- Let her talk. goddamn it.

890
00:51:44.568 --> 00:51:46.670
- Sit down. Hugh!
- No. I'll speak if I want!

891
00:51:46.736 --> 00:51:50.073
Goddamn it. who are you.
Minister of Propaganda?

892
00:51:51.441 --> 00:51:53.810
We suffered for years
under the yoke of that woman.

893
00:51:53.877 --> 00:51:55.612
Years!

894
00:51:55.679 --> 00:51:58.715
She estranged us
from our own daughter.

895
00:51:58.782 --> 00:52:01.585
Ruined I don't know how many
