00:52:11.495 --> 00:52:12.896
Hear. hear.

901
00:52:16.333 --> 00:52:18.568
From beyond the grave even.

902
00:52:20.537 --> 00:52:23.173
This is a woman
who didn't want a funeral.

903
00:52:23.240 --> 00:52:27.611
You all. her children.
you ignored her wishes.

904
00:52:27.677 --> 00:52:29.946
Only after she's dead.
by the way.

905
00:52:33.383 --> 00:52:35.385
She didn't want a funeral.

906
00:52:35.452 --> 00:52:37.954
