Together again.</i>

924
00:54:00.470 --> 00:54:01.871
<i>Oh.</i>

925
00:54:01.938 --> 00:54:05.709
<i>I'm almost glad this happened.</i>

926
00:54:17.020 --> 00:54:18.421
