933
00:54:28.098 --> 00:54:29.299
<i>Right now. He's on his way.</i>

934
00:54:29.366 --> 00:54:31.067
<i>Oh. it's wonderful.</i>

935
00:54:31.134 --> 00:54:32.736
<i>I'll get his room ready.</i>

936
00:54:32.802 --> 00:54:35.538
<i>I knew my baby would come home.</i>

